<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/style.css">
	<title>MadMeme</title>
</head>

<body>
    <hr>
	<h1>MadMeme</h1>
    <hr>
    <form action="/images" method="post">
        <textarea id="top" class="adlib" name="top" rows="10"></textarea><br>
        <label for="top">Top Text:</label><br><br>
        <textarea id="bottom" class="adlib" name="bottom" rows="10"></textarea><br>
        <label for="bottom">Bottom Text:</label><br><br>
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
    <hr>
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <p>
        <b>Using nouns, verbs, adjectives, and adverbs, insert your adlib template in the text area above as in the following example:</b><br><br>
        "The [adjective] [noun] went to the [noun] and [verb] the [noun]."<br><br>
        <b>When you're done, click Submit to generate your memes!</b>
    </p>
</body>

</html>